{"tid":1533523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你自己唔衝，唔該唔好叫人衝","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T18:21:41.000Z","uid":280192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd6157ea2bb5f3230490f37dbcdf2d963573168","tid":1533523,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:44:48.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;自己衝，先去支持人衝。&rdquo;最近呢類講法聽人講唔少。<br />\n<br />\n但我從來無聽過人講，唔該你自己唔返工去踢波，先去支持C朗美斯。<br />\n<br />\n亦無聽人講，唔該你自己日日打籃球，先去支持櫻木、流川。<br />\n<br />\n我地大部分人唔係運動員、科學家或藝術家，但我地都會敬重和支持貝多芬、愛因斯坦。<br />\n<br />\n一切肯付出去追尋夢想嘅人，無論最後是否成功，都值得我地敬重和支持。<br />\n<br />\n22年的沉淪，就係因為衝嘅人，唔夠人支持。<br />\n<br />\n唔係人人可以做勇武，每個人包袱都唔同，但我身為和理非，實在越來越支持前線所做的一切。前線仍然有所顧忌，其中一個主因係怕一做多左，和理非民意就會逆轉，以前又真係發生過。<br />\n<br />\n如此，後排其實都有責任。所以，希望前線明白，和理非今次真係核彈都唔割。我地其實都知道如果輸左，香港變新疆係慘過核爆。<br />\n<br />\n做你地認為啱嘅事就得。"},{"pid":"7db6b8f4a5269472a568fdf3f7a4407047fc1f6a","tid":1533523,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:46:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8/9去美國領事館請願</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">派人道支援/過人權法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3i9E9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3i9E9a.png&h=b678595e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M80cCFS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM80cCFS.png&h=5da9f118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有大量文宣推<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人權法</strong></span><br />\n<strong>請瘋狂tweet and retweet</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3D54td2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3D54td2.png&h=af5cfe54&s={SIZE}\" /><i